From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.local>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 06:29:43 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 2: Instagram OAuth + webhook receiving

- Add Instagram OAuth (Instagram API with Instagram Login): connect,
  callback, and disconnect routes. Exchanges code -> short-lived ->
  60-day long-lived token, stores profile + token against the user.
- Add /api/webhooks/instagram: GET verification handshake, POST
  signature-verified ingestion of inbound DMs into WebhookLog and
  Conversation/Message (no AI reply yet, by design).
- Wire InstagramSettings + Inbox repositories to real Prisma queries,
  replacing Phase 1 in-memory/mock data.
- Schema: unique InstagramSettings.businessAccountId (webhook routing
  key) + tokenExpiresAt; Conversation.instagramSenderId with a
  (userId, instagramSenderId) unique constraint for find-or-create.
- Settings UI: real Connect/Disconnect flow, with a guarded manual
  fallback form that can't accidentally clobber a real OAuth token.
- README: Meta App Dashboard setup steps + end-to-end test checklist.
